       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01  X-COPROJ                      LIKE COPROJ OF PPRJMBR-P.
       01  X-COTPRJ                      LIKE COTPRJ OF PPRJMBR-P.
       01  X-COSLIB                      LIKE COSLIB OF PPRJMBR-P.
       01  X-COSRCN                      LIKE COSRCN OF PPRJMBR-P.
       01  X-COLMBR                      LIKE COLMBR OF PPRJMBR-P.
