     ‚* KOMMANDOZEILE AUFRUFEN
     ‚*--------------------------------------------------------------
       KOMMANDOZEILE SECTION.
       CMD-LIN-00.

           CALL     "XXP2001"
           END-CALL.

       CMD-LIN-90.
           EXIT.
