     ‚*--------------------------------------------------------------
       ANZEIGE-PGM-INFOS SECTION.
       ANZ-PGM-00.

           INITIALIZE F12.
     ‚* INFORMATIONEN ANZEIGEN
           CALL     "CFP0009" USING PGM-WRK
                                    F12
           END-CALL.
           INITIALIZE F12.

       ANZ-PGM-90.
           EXIT.
